    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-11-18T14:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-11-18T14:00:00-05:00" n="410"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d410">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 300.115L22/4</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Germany</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_GJC1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-11-18T14:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 18, 1916, 2 p. m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3587. Department advised that unarmed American steamer <hi rend="italic"
                        >Lanao</hi>, Philippine registry, <hi rend="italic">en route</hi> from
                    Saigon to Havre with cargo of rice was sunk by German submarine October 28, 30
                    miles off Cape Vincent, Portugal. Officers and crew apparently saved.</p>
                <p>Please bring this case to immediate attention of German Government and request
                    investigation and prompt report regarding this sinking of an American
                    vessel.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
